umber of user is roughly equal to the directivity offered by the\nflat top beam system, and illustrates the promise SDMA offers for improving\ncapacity in wireless system. Here multipath fading is not considered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Feb 2010 17:45:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-02-18"}
