 model curve\nfor the gravito-magnetic time delay during one orbital revolution. We suggest\nthat this type of delay will have a larger contribution during the last phase\nof the system evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Feb 2010 05:39:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Sep 2012 17:21:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 4 Sep 2012 13:35:03 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 27 Sep 2012 18:59:24 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Fri, 5 Oct 2012 10:43:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-10-08"}
