id harmonics is\nalso provided for completeness. Convergence conditions are also studied.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Feb 2010 12:15:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Apr 2010 11:01:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 30 Nov 2010 19:37:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-06-21"}
